# Copy this file to `.env.local` and set RABOTA_HH_USER_AGENT.
# Restart `npm run dev` after any change.
#
# Format (single line, no quotes unless your shell requires them):
#   AppName/Version (your-email@domain.com)
# Example:
#   RabotaByParser/1.0 (you@example.com)
#
# Prefer RABOTA_HH_USER_AGENT: some tools set HH_USER_AGENT globally (often with
# blocked patterns). This app reads RABOTA_HH_USER_AGENT first.
#
#   RABOTA_HH_USER_AGENT=YourUniqueApp/1.0 (you@mail.ru)
#
# Optional fallback (ignored by Next if HH_USER_AGENT is already set in the parent process):
#   HH_USER_AGENT=YourUniqueApp/1.0 (you@mail.ru)
#
# HH API rules: https://github.com/hhru/api
